---
title: Bacon & Cabbage Fritters with Sesame Potato Chunks & Japanese Aioli
description: This fritter dish is our take on the popular Japanese 'as you like' savoury pancake. With crunchy cabbage and crisp bacon in the mix, plus a crisp salad and golden potatoes on the side, this mouth-watering meal will be happily devoured by all!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/japanese-bacon-cabbage-fritters-f9af89e8.jpg
